[
    {
        "text": "What if plants could count?",
        "start": 2.53,
        "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
        "text": "The Venus flytrap can —",
        "start": 5.56,
        "duration": 2.11
    },
    {
        "text": "in a way.",
        "start": 7.67,
        "duration": 1.34
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s carnivorous and\nit waits for an insect",
        "start": 9.01,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "to fall in its trap and\ntrip its trigger hairs.",
        "start": 11.75,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Each time a hair is disturbed,\nan electrical signal",
        "start": 15.89,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "travels along cell surfaces.",
        "start": 19.01,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "Scientists wired a\nflytrap with electrodes",
        "start": 21.62,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "so they could see this\nprocess in action.",
        "start": 24.38,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "Each flick produced\nan electric signal",
        "start": 27.44,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "called an action potential.",
        "start": 29.75,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "It took two flicks within\na space of 20 seconds",
        "start": 31.91,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "to make the trap\nsnap shut.",
        "start": 35.27,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "And more than three flicks",
        "start": 38.14,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "to start up\nthe cells that",
        "start": 39.91,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "make the digestive enzymes\nin dissolving the prey.",
        "start": 41.51,
        "duration": 5.46
    },
    {
        "text": "And the more times a\nfrenetic, struggling victim",
        "start": 46.97,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "trips a trigger hair,\nthe more such juices flow.",
        "start": 50.06,
        "duration": 5.42
    },
    {
        "text": "Now that’s a smart plant.",
        "start": 55.48,
        "duration": 2.48
    }
]